item.title: A Vestibule For Expansion
item.description: A Vestibule For Expansion April 16th, 2018, A young bare faced boy jaunted into his new workplace. Greeted warmly, he proceeded to receive a tour of this strange new environment. After a brief overview of the facility, he was led to his new office. Yes, his very own office. With his own computer, and desk. This was a monumentally novel experience. To have ones own office was indeed strange, yet added only to the excitement of the experience.
